Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這位新號碼在小學\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So our new number's in this grade school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中之一是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}One of them, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾西·布克  八歲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tracie Booker, eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的號碼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We received her number
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她十四歲的哥哥馬爾科姆的號碼同時跳出\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}along with that of her 14-year-old brother, Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發了  看你手機\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Here, check your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是家庭問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Could be dealing with a domestic issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到他們媽媽了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have you located their mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈森大街1412號  里克島\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}1412 Hazen Street, Rikers Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕他們的母親在監獄里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm afraid their mother's in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪名是非法持械\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}on a weapons violation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親已故  沒發現任何親屬\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The father's deceased and I have yet to locate any relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他們都在政府系統中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So they're in the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄養兒童\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Foster children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來他們的生活中  那所學校是唯一不變的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It seems that school is the one constant in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就變了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處找不到特蕾西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's no sign of Tracie anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許她的同學會知道她在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps a fellow student knows where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人肯跟警察開口的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No one's gonna get caught dead talking to a cop,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這一片不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}not in this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思了  我可是輕而易舉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Funny, I didn't have any problems
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓馬爾科姆的朋友開口了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}getting Malcolm's friends to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  他們是有人問我要號碼來著\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Although, one of them did ask me for my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到馬爾科姆了嗎  肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have you located Malcolm, Ms. Shaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今天沒上學\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He didn't show for school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你不得不施展魅力了  約翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Looks like you're gonna have to work your magic after all, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們今天看到特蕾西·布克了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}have any of you seen Tracie Booker today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,條子  我們走吧  姑娘們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}5-0. Let's go, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我陪你們玩這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, I'll play you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hopscotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別閃了你的老腰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't go hurting yourself, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要我們透信兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Want us to drop a dime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給點錢錢啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It'sgonnacost ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息  哈羅德  我有消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Good news, Harold, I got a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞消息  我還要小額備用金\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Bad news, I need more petty cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得提醒你  里瑟先生  我們現在的存款\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Need I remind you, Mr. Reese, that our recent deposit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須撐好長一段時間啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}has to last for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得提醒你每天早上送特蕾西來上學\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Malcolm walks Tracie to school every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在沿著他們的路線走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm retracing their route.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個孩子分別上不同的學校  彼此離得很遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The children go to separate schools across town from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要天一亮就出發才能準時到校\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They'd have to leave at the crack of dawn to be on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我們是遲到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think we're the ones who are too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛看到一犯罪現場\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just stumbled on a crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿孩子們不在這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's hope the kids aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑幫槍戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We have a gang-related shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三名成年非裔美國人和三名亞美尼亞人身亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Three adult, African-americans and three Armenians, deceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩名男性受多處槍傷\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Two males with multiple gsws.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你破壞證據了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you're tampering with our evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊利警探  兇案組的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Detective Riley, homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倫諾克斯特工  緝毒局的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Agent Lennox, DEA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是我的搭檔  湯姆森\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is my partner, Thomsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她出什么事兒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What exactly happened her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常我會說讀報告去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Normally, I'd say you can read it in our report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過既然你如此彬彬有禮  我也不吝分享了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But since you asked so nice, I'm willing to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣  萊利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Knock yourself out, Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上報去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll call it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字幕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No colors, no bandanas, and no ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是兄弟會\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's the Brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽說過\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來他們跟亞美尼亞人有毒品交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It appears they were making a drug trade with the Armenians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像唯一交易成功的只有子彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Looks like the only thing they traded were bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么岔子了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說兄弟會的老大態度非常強硬\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've heard the Brotherhood's leader strikes a hard bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許亞美尼亞人不喜歡他的談判方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe the Armenians didn't like his negotiation tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dominic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緝毒局數月來一直在查他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}DEA's been trying to lay eyes on him for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有進展  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No luck. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克老謀深算\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dominic's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他讓手下出面負責毒品交易  承擔風險\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He let's his men handle the drug deals and the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有誰活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who's left standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個亞美尼亞人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Armenian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕他也熬不過今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Doubt he'll make it through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個打手被射傷\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And a piece of muscle with a gunshot wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多米尼克的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}One of Dominic's boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是  他也不肯開口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Unfortunately, he's not talking either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來兄弟會雇他不是沖著他能說會道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guessing the Brotherhood didn't hire him for his conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有個鬧不明白的地方  萊利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got a puzzle here, Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了兩輛車\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got two four-seater vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八個黑幫分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}eight gangsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一大袋海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and one large bag of heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒找到買毒品的錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Only piece missing is the drug money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們把這棟樓和那兩輛車翻了個遍  就是找不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We tossed this building and the cars, it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰拿走了錢呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So who took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按海洛因的行情\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Given the street value of the heroin,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個問題價值50萬美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd say that's the $1/2 million question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不管誰拿走了錢  都活不到今天晚上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm betting whoever it is won't make it till sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倫諾克斯特工  過來看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Agent Lennox, got something you should see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警探  我們有麻煩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Detective, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我通過政府發放的交通卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've managed to track the booker children
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了布克家的小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}via their government issued metro cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們從第五大道車站出的站\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They exited the 5th Avenue Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五大道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}5th Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不認為這些孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You don't suppose the children
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃學是為了去購物吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}ditched school to go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是湊巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Funny you should mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們正在買新衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They're buying new clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來是這兩個孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It would appear that the children
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷了毒品錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}have stolen the drug money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能先攔下他們嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Think you can intercept them before anyone else does?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我盡量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去洗手間\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I need to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能憋著嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can't you hold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬爾科姆  特蕾西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Malcolm? Tracie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你攔下他們了嗎  教授\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You got the kids, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟丟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望別是永遠地丟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I hope it's not for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩孩子比想象中聰明得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The children have proven more resourceful than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們吸引太多注意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But their antics have raised more than a few eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么發展下去  用不了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}At this rate, it won't be long
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟會就會找到他們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}before the Brotherhood catches up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有亞美尼亞人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not to mention the Armenians.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許你該找緝毒局幫幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps you should enlist the help of the DEA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經告訴倫諾克斯特工馬爾科姆和特蕾西的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I already told Agent Lennox about Malcolm and Tracie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經發布了對兩個孩子的協查通報\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's a B.O.L.O. out for the kids now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不敢想象如果黑幫比我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I shudder to think what will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先找到這些孩子會發生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}if the gangs find them before we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱們就先下手為強\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So let's beat the perps to the punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先阻止他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Stop them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What exactly do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給肖找了點活干\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got a little job for Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這活兒需要點醫療經驗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It requires some medical experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你該去見位老朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I think it's time you caught up with an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  哈羅德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hello, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得承認  我很懷念和你對弈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I must confess, I've missed our little chess matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近忙什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where have you been keeping yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么說吧  我決定重返校園了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guess you could say that I've decided to go back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在學術界定能如魚得水\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I imagine you'd fit in rather well in academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你卻跑來這兒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And yet, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道丟失了毒品錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've heard about the missing drug money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被幾個小賊偷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and the little thieves who stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰正在想辦法保護那些孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}John's trying to get the children to safety
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他需要時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but he needs time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我再一次扮演次仲裁人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you want me to play mediator again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我們欠你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We would be in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們已經欠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以控制亞美尼亞人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can control the Armenians.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過兄弟會你們得自己解決\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you'll have to deal with the Brotherhood yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰認為你已經\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}John seemed to think that you've tried to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯系過他們的老大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}contact their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克  他很難找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dominic, he's proven to be elusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許比你還難找  哈羅德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps even more elusive than you, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是個搭地鐵的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm just a man on a subway train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不起眼的老師\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A humble teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我角色我扮演過\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I played that role once myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而約翰現在是警探了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And John's a detective now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好奇  為什么突然轉換身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm curious, why the sudden career shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事改變了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徹底改變了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something fundamental.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在說\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I'm not just referring
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的朋友的行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to how you and your friends operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你知道發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think you know what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你應該欠我的  應該告訴我真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I think you owe it to me to tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時代雖然改變了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Times may have changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是恐怕你我都行走在黑暗中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but I'm afraid we're both in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華爾街站到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is Wall Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一站富爾頓街\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Next stop is Fulton Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要站在關閉的車門前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Stand clear of the closing doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你主動申請了個七殺案\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You volunteered us for a septuple homicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七殺是死了七個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Septuple as in seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你要我好好工作的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're the one who told me to take this job seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要努力工作  記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Be hands on, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得  那是叫你努力搞好文件工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, then you can get your "hands on" some of this paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意風度啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where are your manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒看到倫洛克斯特工在等我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can't you see that Agent Lennox is waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是唯一一個找你的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's not the only one looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那朋友  林克\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your friend, Link?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逮捕的那個兄弟會副手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The Brotherhood lieutenant you arrested--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分鐘前被放出來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}released from the joint ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟會找了個未成年的混混\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Brotherhood found an underage corner boy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去替他背黑鍋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to take the fall for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子把罪都認了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kid confessed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林克只受到輕罪指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Link's getting off with a misdemeanor charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"事后從犯"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"Accessory after the fact."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍后再對付他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll deal with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好他會先對付你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not if he deals with you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空嗎  警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got a minute, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信任真是件有趣的事  萊利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Trust is a funny thing, Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微調查了你一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I did a little digging on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在當緝毒警之前沒什么資料\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Couldn't find much before your stint in narco.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你不像個兇案警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know, you don't strike me as a homicide detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是你查得不夠努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Well, maybe you're not looking hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外  考慮到你的經歷\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Surprising, given someone of your experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從安納波利斯畢業  班級第一\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You graduated from Annapolis, top of your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在美國海軍服役兩期  表現優異\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Served two tours, with distinction, for the U.S. Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后加入了緝毒局\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}before joining the DEA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我也做了點調查\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, I did a little digging too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你是打算站在那兒審問我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So you just gonna stand there and interrogate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是討論一下案子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or would you like to discuss this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對兄弟會有何了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How well do you know the Brotherhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我逮捕了他們的一個成員\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I arrested one of their soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你應該知道他們的網絡無所不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then you know their network's as pervasive as it is deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不守什么地盤\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They don't believe in territories,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的線人滲透了每個街區\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}they've got informants on every block,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  恐怕是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and, I'm afraid to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也滲透了各執法部門\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in every law enforcement organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緝毒局認為局里有內鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The DEA believes there's a mole in our agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人為多米尼克工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A man working for Dominic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-知道是誰嗎  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Any idea who? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白說  這讓我和我的搭檔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Frankly, it has me and my partner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始懷疑我們的同事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}looking sideways at our colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在卻還是信任我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yet you're trusting me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過  信任是件有趣的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Like I said, trust is a funny thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只感覺你與眾不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something tells me you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你充滿熱忱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你跟我分享了關于孩子的線索\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And since you shared your lead with me on the kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是今天早些時候拍的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This was taken earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么孩子偷了50萬美元之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What kind of kids steal $1/2 million
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一件事是去買新衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and the first thing they buy are new clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許他們要去什么有著裝要求的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe they're going somewhere with a dress code.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們買其他東西了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They buy anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們用現金買了一個手機\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They purchased a phone with cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能追蹤嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can you trace it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要有序列號就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All I need is a serial number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經申請搜查令了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Already applied for a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾小時就能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Should only take a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我們沒有幾個小時了  里瑟先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm afraid we may not have a couple of hours, Mr. Reese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好我們認識一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then it's a good thing we know someone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能黑進孩子手機的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}who can hack the kids' phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這比以前要難辦得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's considerably more difficult than it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前有手機生產商的資料\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was up on the cell phone providers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但跟圖書館一起失去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but I lost that capability along with the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須從頭開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll have to start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就期盼肖有好運氣吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's hope Shaw's having better luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在醫院嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃有變\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不去普通醫院了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're not going to general.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正醫療水平也不怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Care's sub-par anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是急救人員\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You ain't no EMT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是警察嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有名字嗎  硬漢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You got a name, tough guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥們都叫我迷你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Boys call me Mini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我塊頭大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}'cause I'm big.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  大塊頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, supersize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你給你哥們林克打電話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I want you to call your pal, Link.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問出他的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get his location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干你們這行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guy like you in your line of work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能認出真正的殺手  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know a killer when you see one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道這個號碼的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah? How'd you get this number?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林克  我是迷你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You, Link, it's Mini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你跟亞美尼亞人有點麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The word is you got into some trouble with the Armenians.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都在掌控中\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nothing that couldn't be handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where you at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去百老匯街和里德街路口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Boys are gonna be there at Broadway and Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分鐘后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  猛男  這事兒很簡單\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, tough guy, I'm gonna make this real simple for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照我說的做  你就能活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You do what I say, you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下車\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別打什么鬼主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And don't get any ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扳機比你動作快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}this trigger is faster than your first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我通過手機定位到了孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've located the children via their cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的是  他們好像往一個大律所去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Oddly, they appear to be headed toward a large law office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地址是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's the address?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有多遠  我的腳痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How much further? My feet hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你說了要買舒服點的鞋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I told you to buy sensible shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么我們不能像普通人那樣從前門進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why can't we just go through the front like normal people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為普通人不會背著一大包現金  知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}'cause normal people don't carry bags of cash, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前門有保安\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Front's got security.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那里進去  他們會把錢拿走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We go up there, they take our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這也不是我們的錢啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But it's not really our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我們拿了錢的那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Those guys we took it from--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  他們不能傷害我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A'ight, they can't hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來  這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Come on! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有兩分鐘  頂多三分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We got about two minutes, three minutes tops
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后警察就該來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}till the cherries roll in.
