Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我們運氣不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Well, lucky for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道誰能找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got an idea who knows where to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  咱們走走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, let's take a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把多米尼克的事都告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're gonna tell me everything you know about Dominic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別緊張  我朋友們很快就會來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Relax. My friends will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手機上有《我的世界》嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You got Minecraft on that phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個侄女跟你差不多大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got a niece your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定你能找到喜歡的游戲玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sure you'll be able to find something to play with on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你外表兇  人很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know, you're nicer than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子好像挺喜歡你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kid seems to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我忍不住想  我真的可以有所成就\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Makes me think I might actually be making a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜猜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let me guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很久沒有過這種感覺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You haven't felt that way in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能幫他們  但緝毒局有太多繁文縟節\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I could help them, but the DEA has so much red tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無能為力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一直等到他們錄完口供  交出證據\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Till they make a statement and hand over evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你要說什么  免了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Look, I know what you're gonna say, all right, so save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會告訴你錢在哪里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm not telling you where that money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用說\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You won't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們總會找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We'll find it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我們怎么找到你和你妹妹的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How do you think we found you and your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有監控設備\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Y'all got cameras and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  追蹤你不會花太久的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, won't take long to retrace your steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么說我現在該做筆交易嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Saying I should make a deal now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁你還有籌碼可以討價還價\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}While you still have something to barter with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你犯了一些致命的錯誤  馬爾科姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've made some very big mistakes, Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群黑幫朝我們掃射時\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, I kind of realized that when those gangsters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就意識到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}were shooting at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能阻止他們嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can you stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm gonna try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你之前已經逮捕一個了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you've already arrested one of them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但兄弟會利用街頭小混混\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but the Brotherhood uses corner boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些比你大不了多少的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}kids not much older than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替他們蹲監獄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to get them out of prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都有自己的立場  我為什么要相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Look, everybody got an angle, why should I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我身處你和他們之間\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}'Cause I'm the one standing between you and them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬爾科姆  你說你是男子漢  有計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Malcolm, you say you're "the man with the plan,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我看到的只是一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but all I've seen is a thief
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點害死妹妹的賊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that's almost got his sister killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想當男子漢嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You wanna be the man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先照顧好你的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Start taking care of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什么不測\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Anything happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你照顧好小特\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You take care of T.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答應我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有錢都在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All the money's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.01,0:22:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我們買衣服花掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Except for what we spent on clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信緝毒局能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sure the DEA will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很對\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支援隨時會來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Back up will be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶你妹妹去一下衛生間  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get your sister and make sure she uses the bathroom, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子很聰明  湯姆森會來接的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kid's smart. Thomsen'll pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先確保沖出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need to make it out of here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll do a sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I should go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防兄弟會的人等著\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In case the Brotherhood's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你擔心我嗎  警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You worried about me, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒你幫助  我也走到了今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I made it this far without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  迷你  坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, Mini, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己拷到管子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Cuff yourself to the pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.27,0:24:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得看情況了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我想知道的事  就是休息區\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You tell me what I want to know, it's a pit-stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告訴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的安息區\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}it's your final resting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now where's Dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎樣  小姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What you gonna do, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打我一頓拷問我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You gonna beat it out of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.05,0:24:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你不這樣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Isn't that what you would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.38,0:24:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必多問\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why bother asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.72,0:24:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我  我們不是一類人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You and me, we ain't even close to the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.16,0:24:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.64,0:24:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有種預感你能忍受疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got a hunch you can take the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至樂在其中  就像我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You might even enjoy it. Like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.65,0:24:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們要做朋友嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So now we gonna be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.76,0:24:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去你可以稍微利用下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Seems like you could use a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.11,0:24:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同伴知道我抓了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your boys know I have you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克怎么沒派人來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}so how come Dominic hasn't sent anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.14,0:24:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許因為他知道我自己能解決\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe 'cause he knows I can handle my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.63,0:24:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許你只是不值得讓他們找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or maybe you're just not worth the gas it takes to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.28,0:24:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在休克的第一階段\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're in the first stages of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.61,0:25:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出汗  細脈  失去血色\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sweaty, thready pulse, loss of color.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.00,0:25:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在要么死撐到血流光\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now, you can either stall until you bleed out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.64,0:25:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么告訴我多米尼克在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or you can just tell me where Dominic is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是說了  你覺得我會怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If I tell you, what do you think will happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.87,0:25:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是死在另一個地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just end up in another basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告訴我他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You give me his location,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.53,0:25:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就放你出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I will get you out of dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.80,0:25:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說吧  迷你  放聰明點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Come on, Mini, be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戲玩久一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Play the long game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這樣的人  游戲玩不久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ain't no long game for guys like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.37,0:25:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是游戲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.56,0:25:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他媽怎么做都一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Doesn't make a damn bit of a difference what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.93,0:25:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥做都一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or who you do it for.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dominic ain't no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.94,0:25:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他人沒區別\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just another man like all the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.60,0:25:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼克似乎要比你說得聰明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sounds like this Dominic's a lot smarter than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.37,0:25:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多幾年  他就會下臺\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Couple years on top, he'll burn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.39,0:25:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者送命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or get wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.90,0:25:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一條真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Only one rule:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.57,0:25:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們最終都難逃一死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We all die in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.15,0:25:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倫諾克斯特工已經走好一會了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Agent Lennox's been gone awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.25,0:26:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是不是遇到麻煩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Think she ran into trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.19,0:26:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人之前肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got a feeling that woman's stared trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.95,0:26:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷過不少風浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in the face more than a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.76,0:26:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sure she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.89,0:26:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  萊奈爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's up, Lionel?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.78,0:26:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以請  我吃牛排來謝我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, you can--uh--thank me with a prime rib,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.26,0:26:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者雙烤土豆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe some twice-baked potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.48,0:26:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在點餐呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You placing a dinner order,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.95,0:26:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是有什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or is there a reason for your call?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.28,0:26:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你硬塞給我的那樁七殺案\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know that septuple homicide you saddled me with?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.64,0:26:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在一部手機上發現條線索\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got a lead off one of the cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個電話號碼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A number.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.87,0:26:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟會的人在兇案現場打了這個電話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Brotherhood banger called it from the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.24,0:26:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.03,0:26:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你不想和多米尼克對話嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So didn't you want to have a chat with Dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.84,0:26:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可能是他的號碼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This could be his number.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.41,0:26:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你只有一次機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you'll only get to call it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.27,0:26:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就打打看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Better make that call then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.29,0:26:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么會有這個手機\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where'd you get that phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.98,0:26:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倫諾克斯特工給我的  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Agent Lennox gave it to me, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.38,0:26:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  搭檔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is there a problem, partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.25,0:26:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來緝毒緝局的確有兄弟會內鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Seems the DEA does have a mole working for the brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.92,0:26:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倫諾克斯特工騙了我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Agent Lennox double-crossed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.99,0:26:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還保證呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Gave me your word huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.74,0:26:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么說是沒有支援了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So we don't have back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.21,0:26:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有支援  只不過要久一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We do, it's just gonna take a little longer than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.96,0:27:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撐住  我馬上來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sit tight. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.77,0:27:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You'd better make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.75,0:27:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們被包圍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.52,0:27:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有緝毒局內線的最新情況嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have you heard from our snitch in the DEA, lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.84,0:27:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  不過她說警察和孩子就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, but she said the cop and the kid are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.15,0:27:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉上嘴  就饒你一命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Keep your mouth shut and you'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.87,0:27:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  弗斯科預計多久到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Finch, you got an ETA on Fusco?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.87,0:27:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八分鐘  視交通狀況而定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Eight minutes based on current traffic patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.45,0:27:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能把兄弟會拖到那時么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can you hold off the Brotherhood until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.42,0:27:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正有此意\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.65,0:27:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想倫諾克斯女士拿到毒品錢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I imagine Ms. Lennox has recovered the drug money by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.44,0:27:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她是內鬼  兄弟會為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But if she's their mole, then why is the Brotherhood
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.31,0:27:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在追殺孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}still after the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.55,0:27:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能她不止騙了我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps we're not the only ones she's double-crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.48,0:27:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她留下了手機\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Would explain why she left her cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.52,0:27:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟會就追蹤不到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So the Brotherhood can't trace her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.19,0:27:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸  我們也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nor can we, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.91,0:27:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十萬足夠讓人失蹤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}$1/2 million is more than enough to disappear for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.78,0:27:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就沒這么幸運\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're not so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.07,0:28:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟會拿不到錢不會罷手的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Brotherhood's not backing down without their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.59,0:28:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退而求其次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What about the next best thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.46,0:28:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖女士  你有多米尼克的位置了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ms. Shaw, have you located dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.16,0:28:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.64,0:28:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我和大塊頭談了談\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I had a chat with our big friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.74,0:28:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留他一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}left him alone to cool off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.42,0:28:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那些冒火的同伙沒來找他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That guy's angry his boys ain't come looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.32,0:28:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來救名打手不是他們的首要任務\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guess saving a piece of muscle's not high on their priority list.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.18,0:28:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們該重新考慮下任務的重要性了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They should rethink their priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.99,0:28:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大塊頭氣得想干架\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Muscle's gonna be looking for a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.89,0:28:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得他會去找多米尼克算賬\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you think he'll confront dominic?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.76,0:28:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得他已經火冒三丈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think he's just mad enough to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.79,0:28:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大塊頭是條小魚  但他能引出大魚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Our guy's a little fish, but he could lead us to the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.64,0:28:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把小魚放回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So throw the minnow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You two ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.58,0:28:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要沖了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.19,0:28:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改主意了  我不想走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I changed my mind. I don't wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.77,0:28:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾西  水槍還在嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tracie, do you still have your squirt gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.01,0:28:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.39,0:28:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以備用\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Could come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.31,0:28:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要玩躲貓貓\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}'cause we're gonna play hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.51,0:28:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.46,0:28:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這游戲我擅長\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm really good at this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.17,0:29:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子躲在樓頂房間\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kids are holed up in the penthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.40,0:29:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關掉攝像頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kill the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.95,0:29:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What the--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.23,0:29:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊  他們正往上來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This way. They're coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.96,0:29:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.21,0:29:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察在我媽那里搜到的槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That gun the cops found on my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.32,0:29:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.67,0:30:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽撒了謊  說槍是她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My mom lied. She said it belonged to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.48,0:30:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是我  她根本不會蹲監獄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She wouldn't even be in jail if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.35,0:30:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要槍做什么  馬爾科姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why'd you have a gun, Malcolm?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.05,0:30:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是為了自保\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just wanted to protect my own.
