Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先逃出去  再來擔心下邊的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's get out of here and we'll worry about the rest later.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.08,0:30:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.44,0:30:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到他了嗎  哈羅德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You got him, Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.84,0:30:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他行動了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He's on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.23,0:30:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人欽佩  肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm impressed, Ms. Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.93,0:30:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大塊頭很強悍啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, big guy was strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.02,0:30:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧還流了這么多血\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}considering how much blood he lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.86,0:30:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  我還松了松管子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Course, I did loosen the pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.11,0:30:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我指的是你放置了追蹤設備\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was referring to how you were able to plant a tracking device
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.56,0:30:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒被他察覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}without our friend noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.13,0:30:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也給你安了  還有弗斯科\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I planted one on you, Fusco...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.83,0:31:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠  還有約翰呢  至今沒被發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hell, even John. Haven't been caught yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.69,0:31:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不詳詢你的手法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Remind me to stop inquiring about your modus operandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.46,0:31:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.44,0:31:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.52,0:31:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.12,0:31:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是那個算計我們的小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You the dude that maced us?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.61,0:31:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.82,0:31:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's okay.
