Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.59,0:31:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把家伙滑過來  不然這小個兒開花\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Slide that piece over here. Or shorty springs a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.79,0:31:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Easy guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.67,0:31:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是紐約警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm NYPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.30,0:31:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們知道你  萊利警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We know who you are, Detective Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.83,0:31:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見過我的搭檔嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have you met my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.37,0:31:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸會啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.81,0:31:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高興你趕來了  萊納爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Glad you could make it, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.39,0:31:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文件工作麻煩你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sorry about all the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.89,0:31:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥已經麻木了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, I'm getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.10,0:32:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人沒完沒了啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}These guys don't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.41,0:32:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們永遠不可能安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We ain't never gonna be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.93,0:32:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶你妹妹躲起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Take your sister and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.20,0:32:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.70,0:32:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還有幾發\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How many rounds you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.85,0:32:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望足夠\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Enough, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.00,0:32:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子  別哭  你會沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hey, kiddo, don't cry, you're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.69,0:32:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是為這個哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's not why I'm crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.15,0:32:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該永遠在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're supposed to stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.39,0:32:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊納爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Lionel...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬爾科姆人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's Malcolm?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.46,0:32:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當男子漢  得有計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wanna be the man, gotta have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.12,0:32:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在里面嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.57,0:32:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的話最好值得一聽  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You better have something to say worth hearing, little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.12,0:32:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有你想要的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.76,0:32:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做個交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I wanna make a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.54,0:33:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命換我妹妹的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My life for my sister's.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.59,0:33:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說重點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Best be getting to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.96,0:33:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的錢呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's my money?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.58,0:33:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在我這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.34,0:33:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我肯為你工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I'll work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.29,0:33:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你手下的混混\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Be your corner boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.04,0:33:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你頂罪  隨便\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Take a fall for you, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.83,0:33:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放過我妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just leave my sister be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.74,0:33:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他上來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.27,0:33:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你告過別了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I hope you said your good-byes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.45,0:33:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你忘了什么東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think you're forgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.30,0:34:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要錢嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you want your money?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.19,0:34:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You deal with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.47,0:34:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回頭再聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We'll be catching up real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.85,0:34:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想糾正錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was just trying to make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.19,0:34:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用錯誤去糾正錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You can't make something right by doing something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.48,0:34:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證過\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.51,0:34:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  照顧好你妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Go, you take care of your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.59,0:34:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說完了  警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You done, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.88,0:34:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們得好好敘敘舊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We got a lot of catching up to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.49,0:34:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長夜漫漫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hell of a night for a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.78,0:34:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He's clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.98,0:35:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱別每次見面都這樣啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We have got to stop meeting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.72,0:35:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢轉過身來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Turn around nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.09,0:35:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們來這兒不止是為了洗衣服吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe you guys do more than your laundry here.
