Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.26,0:35:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米尼得想辦法運走藏貨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dominic's found a way to move a lot of smack.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.99,0:35:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道該干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know the drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.10,0:35:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里哪個角落最不顯眼呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now where's the one place no one bothers to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.07,0:36:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道不  今天是我的好日子啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What do you know, it's my lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.35,0:36:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰上買一贈一了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got a twofer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.01,0:36:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢找回來了  還抓到了把我丟牢子里的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Our money and the man that incarcerated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.03,0:36:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拿著一個就很好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I guess one out of two ain't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.61,0:36:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where is it?
