Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.51,0:36:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子彈我多得是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I got enough brass to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.75,0:36:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天還是我的好日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Like I said, it's my lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.47,0:36:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.42,0:36:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等這電話等好久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've been expecting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.37,0:36:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚釣得怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How was the fishing trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.93,0:36:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒找到多米尼克\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Came up empty on Dominic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.09,0:36:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我另有發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But--uh-- I found something else
