Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.53,0:37:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,談判會\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The negotiation party.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.09,0:37:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放了萊利警官  不許再糾纏布克兄妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Release Detective Riley and forget about the Booker kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.36,0:37:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是不答應呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What if I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.72,0:37:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就會伐開心  要燒房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or I huff, and I puff, and I burn your house down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.54,0:37:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你也不希望老大知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I don't think you wanna tell your boss
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.13,0:37:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你眼睜睜地看著他的藏貨化為灰燼吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that you watched his stash go up in flames, now, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.73,0:37:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以放警探走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Say I let the detective go...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.17,0:37:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你憑什么保證你就不會動手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}how do I know you're gonna back off?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.85,0:37:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你留份分手禮物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll leave you a parting gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.44,0:37:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷你陪著你的毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mini here can keep your drugs company.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.09,0:37:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來今天不是你的好日子啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guess it's not your lucky day after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.01,0:38:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒說你為誰干活兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Never said who you worked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.96,0:38:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我沒說過\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're right. I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.28,0:38:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你老大  回見\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tell your boss I'll be seeing him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.13,0:38:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上學真的沒問題嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You sure you're okay to go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.33,0:38:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了  你沒事  我就沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Told you. I'm okay if you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我  我們要永遠在一起  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You and me. We stick together, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.82,0:38:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  明天見\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All right, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.55,0:38:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪兒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.98,0:38:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以后每天都能見到特蕾西了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Actually, you'll be seeing Tracie later today.
