Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.29,0:38:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你就會被接到一個新家  你們倆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've been assigned a new home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.47,0:38:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.77,0:38:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你死了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}For a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.28,0:38:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林克怎么會放你走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How'd you get Link to let you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.66,0:38:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很有說服力啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Turns out I can be pretty persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.07,0:38:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.96,0:38:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你聯系了一名律師\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I got you a consultation with a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.81,0:39:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高手  哈佛畢業的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Dream team. Harvard law.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.37,0:39:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}萊絲麗·奎爾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.41,0:39:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多材料可以給她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got a few articles I could send her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.07,0:39:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊恩杰·羅姆一案  還有布萊恩·艾肯一案\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The people versus Ryan Jerome, or the Brian D. Aitken's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.07,0:39:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}前者為強奸  后者為撫養權案
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.02,0:39:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎  馬爾科姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know what, Malcolm?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.76,0:39:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你一定能成為一個好律師\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think you'd make a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.11,0:39:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想當警察呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was thinking about being a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.85,0:39:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.80,0:39:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你  不過我會少突突人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Like you, but I'd shoot less people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.52,0:39:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當男子漢  得有計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wanna be the man, gotta have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.85,0:39:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情提醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As a friendly reminder,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.90,0:39:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請乘客們站在黃色安全線后候車\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}all passengers, please stand beind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.79,0:39:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里有人坐嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This seat taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.63,0:39:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個自由的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's a free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.53,0:39:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起碼曾經是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}At least it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.80,0:39:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有心事嗎  哈羅德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something troubling you, Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.92,0:39:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次見面時  你問了我個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The last time we met, you asked me a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.34,0:39:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你撒謊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.39,0:40:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕真相會陷你于致命危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm afraid the truth would put you in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你這么關心我  哈羅德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I didn't know you cared, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.83,0:40:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我經常有致命危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've been in danger before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.25,0:40:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這次完全不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, this is something altogether different.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.17,0:40:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能說  你說對了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All I can say is, you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.41,0:40:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界已經改變\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.40,0:40:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是回不去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I suppose there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.34,0:40:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我來找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Which brings me to the reason I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.21,0:40:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}《隱身人》  赫·喬·威爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.65,0:40:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗示嗎  哈羅德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A hint, Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.37,0:40:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多事之秋的一點建議\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Advice for these troubled times.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.26,0:40:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一點答謝禮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And a little thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.07,0:40:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}紐約市阿斯托利亞36號大街  33-191
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.68,0:40:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟會的藏貨地址  至少五小時前是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's the location of the Brotherhood's stash house as of five hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.31,0:40:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒品這會兒肯定轉移了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No doubt, the drugs have been relocated by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.78,0:40:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我知道你熱衷于調查對手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I know how dedicated you are to studying your adversaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.21,0:40:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你想知道我是否知道了多米尼克的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I suppose you'll want to know if I identify this Dominic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.20,0:40:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.02,0:41:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時局變幻莫測啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's a tricky business.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.69,0:41:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場游戲要在一團迷霧中玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Playing a game in which you're unsure of the pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.84,0:41:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這場游戲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And in this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.95,0:41:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕根本輸不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I fear that losing is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.94,0:41:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠  你是貓吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Damn, you like a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.99,0:41:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少九條命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You got at least nine lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.73,0:41:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏貨應該是沒保住吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was worried we gonna lose the stash though.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.22,0:41:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洛因很安全  起碼現在是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"H" is safe. For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.73,0:41:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那賤人逼你說出地址了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Bitch made you tell her the location?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.31,0:41:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小妞一直跟蹤我  甩不掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Chick was tracking me. I couldn't shake her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.06,0:41:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能給她點真料  她才肯罷休\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I had to lead her to something of value so she'd back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.53,0:41:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想派人去救你  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I would have sent somebody for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.23,0:41:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你只能聽命行事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you were just following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.98,0:41:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他的叛徒也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I wish his rat would have did the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.96,0:42:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她偷貨時候被我抓個正著\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I caught this chick stealing crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.42,0:42:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以解釋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.15,0:42:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們老大呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's your boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.56,0:42:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛見到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You just met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.38,0:42:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}Every day I see you looking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.48,0:42:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們總是低估你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They always underestimate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.02,0:42:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布克那孩子也偷了我們的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Booker kids stole from us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.55,0:42:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子倒是挺有頭腦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Little man's got a good head on his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.59,0:42:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適合給我們干活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kind of kid should be working for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.19,0:42:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做通他母親的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Spring his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.34,0:42:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他知道誰才是背后老大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Make sure he knows who pulled the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.50,0:42:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小子會回來投奔我們的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Boy'll find his way back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.67,0:42:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全心全意歸順\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hearts and minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.47,0:42:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個警察萊利呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What about that cop, Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.11,0:42:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那賤人跟他一伙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And that bitch that was helping him.
